<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Aiown v2.5 Compiler & Ecosystem</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --primary-blue: #38bdf8;
            --accent-green: #34d399;
            --text-main: #f1f5f9;
